==English==

===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg}}


#A device used to store [[hat]]s upon. Usually made of wood and standing at least five foot tall, they have a single pole making up most of the height, wih a sturdy base to prevent toppling, and an array of lengthy pegs at the top for placement of hats.

